5.
Question 5
If we used the following to retrieve the rows of a result set, how do we access the column member_id in the result set to be used inside a string?

while($row = $sql->fetch(PDO::FETCH_ASSOC)) {
    // your code here
}

0 / 1 point

$row[member_id]


$row->column[member_id]


$row(member_id)


✔️$row['member_id']


